<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>Dosematic</h1>
  <h2>Dose estimation analysis framework</h2>
	<p>
	A modular scientific software framework created for statistical analysis of dosimetric data.<br>
	Clear user interface allows for quick input of the data, plotting and calculations.
	</p><br>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="row">

<div class="col-md-8">

<div class="container" align="center">
  <ul class="nav nav-pills" role="tablist">
